  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="KT4-kilavi">piriviṭai āṟṟāḷ eṉak kavaṉṟa tōḻikkuk kiḻatti uraittatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">Spoken by HER to the confidante who was anxious that she might not have the strength in the time of separation.</p>
          </div>

        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="KT4">
<l>                nōmeṉ ṉeñcē nōmeṉ ṉeñcē</l>
<l>                yimaitīyp paṉṉa kaṇṇīr tāṅki</l>
<l>                yamaitaṟ kamaintanaṅ kātala</l>
<l>                ramaivila rākuta ṉōmeṉ ṉeñcē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>              Aches my heart. Aches my heart.</l>
<l rend="indent">Lids as if burned by eye-water,<note place="foot">Literally: "in having endured tears like burnt the lids."</note></l>
<l rend="indent">he who was content to be content, our lover,</l>
<l rend="indent">that he should be discontent</l>
        <l rend="indent4">–aches my heart.</l>
        <lg type="alternate" resp="#TVG" sameAs="2-4b">
          <l>He who was content with [our] being content, our lover,</l>
          <l>dispelling eye-water [that is] as if burning [our] eyes,</l>
          <l>	that he should be content [no longer]...</l>
        </lg>

            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
